>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="在chroot环境中运行docker命令">在chroot环境中运行docker命令
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在上个部分完成设置后，只需复制docker命令到test用户目录，并修改相关文件的权限即可&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">cp&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">bin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">docker&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">home&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">test&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">bin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">chmod&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">766&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">var&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">run&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">docker&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">R&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>超级实用的bash技巧</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/p/%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84bash%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</link><pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 18:47:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/p/%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84bash%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://ifindv.github.io/p/%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84bash%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/bash.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 超级实用的bash技巧" />&lt;h2 id="使用screen后台运行gdb">使用screen后台运行gdb
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 创建会话
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">screen -S &amp;lt;SESSION_NAME&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 在screen会话中运行gdb
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">gdb attach &amp;lt;PID&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 按ctrl + a，再按d，将当前会话放入后台
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">crtl + a
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">d
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
